WEBVTT

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:31.000
gapini to'xtatib va yana 
takror-takror eshitishi mumkin.

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:34.000
Agar ular bir necha hafta yoki 
bir necha yillar avval

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:36.000
o'rganishi kerak bo'lgan biror mavzuni

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:39.000
yana takror o'rganmoqchi bo'lsa, 
ular hijolat bo'lib,

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:41.000
akasidan so'rab o'tirishga hojat qolmaydi.

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:44.000
Ular o'sha videolarni ko'rishi mumkin.
Agar zeriksalar, keyingi

00:02:44.000 --> 00:02:46.000
mavzularni ko'rishi mumkin.
O'zlariga qulay

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:51.000
vaqt va maromda ko'rishlari mumkin.
Ehtimol, buning eng qulay bo'lmagani,

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:53.000
avvalambor,

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:55.000
eng birinchi marta yangi g'oyani

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:58.000
tushunish uchun bosh qotirib turganda,
sizga kerak eng oxirgi

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:00.000
narsa boshqa bir insonning,

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:03.000
"Buni tushundingmi?" deb aytishi.
Huddi shu narsa